  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Nagaji&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Serpent's Sense&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>The nagaji's gaze is so intense it stops others in their tracks. Once per day, it can attempt to hypnotize a single target, as per the spell <i>hypnotism </i>(caster level equal to the nagaji's Hit Dice). The DC of this effect is equal to 11 + the nagaji's Charisma modifier. The effects of the hypnotic gaze only last a single round. This racial trait replaces serpent's sense.</p>",
